WHAT CHANGES?

#### Red (increase or above normal) ### 
heading -- background-color: #d4423c;
content -- background-color: #d8827d;

#### Green (decrease or below normal) ### 
heading -- background-color: #3fa255;
content -- background-color: #83c596;

#### Default ### 
heading -- background-color: #777;
content -- background-color: #ccc;

--!>
